content: Britannica Library     Library Patron Remote Log-in Please type in your library borrower card number or code to log in. Please note, your card code may be case sensitive. Log in If you do not know or have access to a borrower card number, please contact your local library system. Public Library Services are only licensed to provide Remote Access to members of the public who are registered library patrons. Please note that access to Britannica Online within Schools, Universities, Corporate/Government Organizations, by users who may be members of the Public Library, is NOT COVERED under the Library license agreement. Britannica Library     Access Britannica Library To access Britannica Library enter the Access ID and Passcode provided by your library. Once you've signed into your library's account, you can sign in to your own personal user account for additional features. Sign In Incorrect Access ID or Passcode Trouble signing in? Contact us. Not a subscriber yet?
